{"title":"Nh\u1eefng smartphone c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 n\u0103m 2015","link":"http:\/\/sohoa.vnexpress.net\/tin-tuc\/doi-song-so\/nhung-smartphone-co-cong-nghe-dot-pha-nam-2015-3335644.html","content":"                <div class=\"fck_detail width_common\">                <p class=\"Normal\"> \t\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c ph\u1ee5 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c m\u1eabu smartphone ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u, t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ra \u0111\u1eddi trong th\u00e1ng 12\/2015. Nh\u1eefng model n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed Tech Awards 2015 do<span>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i mu\u1ed9n \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/span><\/p> <p class=\"Normal\"> \tN\u0103m nay, c\u00f3 ba smartphone \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eed cho gi\u1ea3i \"\u0110i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a n\u0103m\" l\u00e0 LG V10, Microsoft Lumia 950 v\u00e0 Sony Xperia Z5 Premium.<\/p> <p class=\"subtitle\"> \t<a href=\"http:\/\/sohoa.vnexpress.net\/su-kien\/binh-chon-san-pham-2015\/binh-luan\/154-microsoft-lumia-950\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">Microsoft Lumia 950<\/span><\/a><\/p> <table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\"><tbody><tr><td> \t\t\t\t<img alt=\"nhung-smartphone-co-cong-nghe-dot-pha-nam-2015\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"http:\/\/img.f5.sohoa.vnecdn.net\/2015\/12\/30\/tech-2-9714-1451449465.jpg\"><\/td> \t\t<\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p class=\"Normal\"> \tLumia 950 l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Microsoft v\u1edbi Windows 10 Mobile - n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 Windows tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh desktop. T\u00ednh n\u0103ng Continuum cho ph\u00e9p ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u00e1y t\u00ednh b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ngo\u00e0i th\u00f4ng qua dock chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Microsoft ho\u1eb7c Wi-Fi Miracast. C\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c n\u00e0y mang l\u1ea1i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn cu\u1ed9c g\u1ecdi hay tin nh\u1eafn, trong khi \u0111ang tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu PowerPoint ho\u1eb7c l\u01b0\u1edbt web, xem phim tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.<\/p> <p class=\"Normal\"> \tTh\u00fa v\u1ecb h\u01a1n, Lumia 950 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n m\u1ed1ng m\u1eaft v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nhanh, ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111eo k\u00ednh. Microsoft c\u0169ng trang b\u1ecb k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i USB-C tr\u00ean s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m di \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi thay v\u00ec c\u1ed5ng microUSB c\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 s\u1ea1c nhanh c\u0169ng cho ph\u00e9p m\u00e1y n\u1ea1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 50% pin ch\u1ec9 trong 30 ph\u00fat.<\/p> <p class=\"subtitle\"> \t<a href=\"http:\/\/sohoa.vnexpress.net\/su-kien\/binh-chon-san-pham-2015\/binh-luan\/153-lg-v10\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\">LG V10<\/span><\/a><\/p> <table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\"><tbody><tr><td> \t\t\t\t<img alt=\"nhung-smartphone-co-cong-nghe-dot-pha-nam-2015-1\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"http:\/\/img.f5.sohoa.vnecdn.net\/2015\/12\/30\/tech-1-9847-1451449465.jpg\"><\/td> \t\t<\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p class=\"Normal\"> \t\u0110i\u1ec3m \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean LG V10 l\u00e0 camera. Phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n LG G4 t\u1eebng thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u1edbn nh\u1edd\u00a0<span>ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u1ee5p h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc m\u00e1y \u1ea3nh, nh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho \"\u0111\u00e0n anh\" V10 cao c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p> <p class=\"Normal\"> \t<span>V10 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb camera 16 megapixel v\u1edbi c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn l\u1edbn, \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edf \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh f\/1.8 v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng rung OIS ba chi\u1ec1u. \u0110\u00e2y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1eabu smartphone \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u00edch h\u1ee3p ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \"ch\u1ec9nh tay\" khi quay video nh\u01b0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn k\u00eanh \u00e2m thanh, t\u0103ng gi\u1ea3m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng Bitrate cho t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 m\u00e0u K, l\u1ea5y n\u00e9t tay, t\u0103ng gi\u1ea3m ISO... t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 m\u00e1y quay th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5.\u00a0<\/span><span>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh RAM 4 GB, c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea3m bi\u1ebfn v\u00e2n tay v\u00e0 b\u1ed9 x\u1eed l\u00fd \u00e2m thanh Hi-Fi 32-bit, LG V10 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 hai m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 hai camera \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p> <p class=\"subtitle\"> \t<a href=\"http:\/\/sohoa.vnexpress.net\/su-kien\/binh-chon-san-pham-2015\/binh-luan\/155-sony-xperia-z5-premium\"><span style=\"color:#0000ff;\"><span>Sony Xperia Z5 Premium<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/p> <table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"tplCaption\"><tbody><tr><td> \t\t\t\t<img alt=\"nhung-smartphone-co-cong-nghe-dot-pha-nam-2015-2\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"http:\/\/img.f5.sohoa.vnecdn.net\/2015\/12\/30\/tech-3-7157-1451449465.jpg\"><\/td> \t\t<\/tr><\/tbody><\/table><p class=\"Normal\"> \tTrong khi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t m\u1edbi \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho ra m\u1eaft smartphone v\u1edbi m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 2K th\u00ec Sony \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 ph\u00e2n gi\u1ea3i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 4K t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u00ean c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng TV cao c\u1ea5p m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh l\u1edbn.<\/p> <p class=\"Normal\"> \tV\u1ec1 l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh 5,5 inch c\u1ee7a Xperia Z5 Premium n\u00e9t g\u1ea5p b\u1ed1n l\u1ea7n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh iPhone 6s Plus chu\u1ea9n Full HD 1.080p, \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c m\u1eaft th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eadn bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e9t v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1ea3nh. Trang b\u1ecb n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 tr\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfu b\u1eb1ng k\u00ednh th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u1ea3o, khi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh ph\u00f3ng l\u1edbn v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 n\u00e9t.\u00a0<span>T\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Z5 Premium c\u0169ng l\u00e0 smartphone \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Sony v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 20 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.<\/span><\/p> <p class=\"Normal\" style=\"text-align:right;\"> \t<strong><span>Song H\u00e0nh<\/span><\/strong><\/p>              <\/div>                <script type=\"text\/javascript\">                   if(typeof(Parser) != \"undefined\"){                      $('.vne_video').each(function(key, val){                          var videoId = $(this).html().trim();                          var vneVideo = '<div style=\"text-align:center;\"><div class=\"vne_video\">'+videoId+'<\/div><\/div>';                          var parentDom = $(this).parent().get(0).tagName;                          var tableDom = $(this).parent().parent().parent().parent();                          if(parentDom == 'TD' || parentDom == 'td')                   